padding-left: 0.289em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-80" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.87</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-81" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-82" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">r</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-83" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-84" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">d<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-85"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-86" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-87"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-88"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-89" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-90" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.252em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>α</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>ω</mi><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>ω</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></mrow><mi>t</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>1000</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>60</mn></mfrac><mn>120</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>0.87</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>d</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-5">\alpha\ =\frac{\omega-\omega_0}{t}=\frac{\frac{0-1000\times2\pi}{60}}{120}=-0.87\ rads^{-2} </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

<p>আবার,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-7-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>N</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>16</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-128" style="width: 11.723em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.592em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1009.35em, 2.543em, -999.998em); top: -2.047em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-129"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-130" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">N<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-131" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-132" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-133" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">(</span></span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-134"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.846em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.486em, 1001.72em, 4.264em, -999.998em); top: -4.506em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.859em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-135"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-136" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">ω</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-137" style="font-size: 70.7%; top: -3.891em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-140" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">0</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-141" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.85em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.846em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-142" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">)</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-143" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-144" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.207em;">t</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-145" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-146" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.863em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-147" style="font-size: 70.7%; top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-148"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-149" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-150" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.86em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.863em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-151" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-152" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">16</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-153" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.051em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>N</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>ω</mi><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>ω</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>×</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>16</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-7">N=\left(\frac{\omega+\omega_0}{2}\right)\times t\times\frac{1}{2\pi}=16\ </script></span> বার&nbsp;</p>

<div class="gtx-trans-icon">&nbsp;</div>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 3 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>স্থিতি ঘর্ষণ গুণাঙ্ক 0.35 এবং প্রতিক্রিয়া বল 84 N হলে ঘর্ষণ বল-</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>53.2 N</p>
</label>

</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-16-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>v</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>u</mi></mrow><mi>t</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>F</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><mi>m</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; /><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-232" style="width: 13.977em; </span>

overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-544"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-545" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-546"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-547"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-548" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-549" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.202em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>I</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>ω</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>I</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>ω</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msubsup><mi>r</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><msub><mi>ω</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><msub><mi>ω</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>ω</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>×</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>4</mn><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>d</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-35">I_1\omega_1 = I_2\omega_2 \Rightarrow r_1^2 \omega_1 = r^2_2 \omega_2 \Rightarrow \omega_2 = \frac{5 \times (4)^2}{2^2} = 20 \ rads^{-1}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 8 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-36-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>10</mn><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-550" style="width: 1.827em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-43-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>L</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>I</mi><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>10</mn><mn>1000</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0.24</mn><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 17.133em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1017.13em, 2.502em, -999.998em); padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-635" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">I<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-636" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">ω</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-637" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-638" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.39em, 4.141em, -999.998em); overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-658"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.314em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-661"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-663"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-664"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-665" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-666" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>L</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>I</mi><mi>ω</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>ω</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>10</mn><mn>1000</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0.24</mn><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>k</mi><mi>g</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-43">L = I\omega = mr^2\omega = \frac{10}{1000} \times 2^2 \times 6 =0.24 \, kgm^2s^{-1}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 9 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>প্রথম রিং এর জন্য,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-49-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-709" style="width: 9.879em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.076em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.068em, 1008.08em, 2.215em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-710"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-711" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">I<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-712" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-713" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 1.232em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-725" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-726" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-727" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-50-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-734" style="width: 0.658em; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-51-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>k</mi><mi>g</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-737" style="width: 8.322em; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-857" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.184em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-858" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-859" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-860" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 2.188em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.331em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.336em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-62">mg \, (1- sin\theta)</script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 200px; height: 95px;"></p>

<p>এক্ষেত্রে ত্বরণ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-63-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0</mn><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; /><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; /><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-866" style="width: 7.461em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.109em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.395em, 1006.11em, 2.543em, -999.998em); top: -2.211em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-867"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-868" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">0</span><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-869" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.166em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-870" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-871" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">F<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-872" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-873" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-874" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-875" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.166em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-876" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-877" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">i</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-878" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-879" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.203em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>0</mn><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>θ</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-63">0 \, \therefore F = mg \, sin \theta</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.369em; left: 0.458em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-941"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-942"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-943" style="font-size: 70.7%; </label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>হালকা বস্তুর আদিবেগ ধনাত্মক ধরে,&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-70-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>450</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>500</mn><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>80</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mi>v</mi><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-950" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">500</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-951" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-73-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>68</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>802.4</mn><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1002" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1003" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1006" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1007" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.207em;">a</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1008" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1009" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1010" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1013" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">9.8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1014" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1015" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                             <span>Question 14 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি ঘড়ির সেকেন্ডের কাঁটার কৌণিক বেগ-</p>

                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">

</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.62em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.625em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.16</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.994em, 1014.59em, 4.51em, -999.998em); top: -2.211em; left: 0em;"><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-1166" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1167" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1168" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1169" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.215em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1001.76em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1170"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1171"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1172" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">9.27</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 1.764em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1173" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">o</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1174" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1175" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.203em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1176" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">h</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1177" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.53em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.535em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1178" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1179" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">sin</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1180"></span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1181" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1182"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1183" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1184" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1185" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">h</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1186" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1187" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.16</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1188" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.182em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mi>r</mi><mi>g</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>20</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>250</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.16</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>9.27</mn></mrow><mi>o</mi></msup><mo>,</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mn>1</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>θ</mi></mrow><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.16</mn><mi>m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-85">tan\theta=\frac{v^2}{rg}=\frac{{20}^2}{250\times9.8}=0.16 \\ \theta={9.27}^o,\frac{h}{1}=\sin{\theta}\Rightarrow h=0.16m </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.797em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∑</mo><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msubsup><mi>F</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>+</mo><msubsup><mi>F</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><msub><mi>F</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><msub><mi>F</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>c</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>s</mi><msup><mn>120</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>∘</mo></mrow></msup></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><msqrt><mn>7</mn></msqrt><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>N</mi><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mo>;</mo><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>∑</mo><mi>F</mi><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>∑</mo><mi>F</mi></mrow><mi>m</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msqrt><mn>7</mn></msqrt><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-91">\sum F = \sqrt{F^2_1+F^2_2+2F_1 \, F_2 \, cos 120^{\circ}} = 4 \sqrt{7} \, N \, ; \, ma = \sum F \, \therefore \, a = \frac{\sum F}{m} = 2\sqrt{7} \, ms^{-2}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-93-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msup><mi>F</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1345" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1346" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.207em;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1347" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">a</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1348" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1349" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">9.8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1352" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1353" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">17</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1354" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1355" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">6.8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1356" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1357" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">51</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1358" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">N<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>F</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi>F</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>17</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>17</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>6.8</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>51</mn><mi>N</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-93">ma=mg-F^\prime\Rightarrow F^\prime=mg-ma=17\times9.8-17\times6.8=51 N</script></span></p>
</span>

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 18 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>বোরের হাইড্রোজেন পরমাণু মডেলে একটি ইলেকট্রন একটি প্রোটনের চারদিকে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-94-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>5.2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1474" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">11</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1007.46em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 7.461em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1475" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1478" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.969em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1479" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1480"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1481"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1482" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.252em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mi>r</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>9.1</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>31</mn></mrow></msup><mo>×</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>2.18</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mn>6</mn></msup><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>5.2</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>8.32</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></msup><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>N</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-100">F = \frac{mv^2}{r} = \frac{9.1 \times 10^{-31} \times (2.18 \times 10^6)^2}{5.2 \times 10^{-11}} = 8.32 \times 10^{-8} \, N</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

width: 0px; height: 2.325em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.614em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>τ</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>r</mi><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>F</mi><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>c</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>s</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mi>θ</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-104">\tau = r \, F \, cos \left(\frac{\pi}{2}-\theta\right)</script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                            <span>Question 25 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.369em; left: 0.458em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-30"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-31"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-32" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-33" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; </label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text" style="font-weight:bold;">D</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-4-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>187.5</mn><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot;                                                 <span class="fas fa-check"></span>
                                            </div>

                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-5-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi>v</mi></mrow><mi>t</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>F</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><mi>m</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>187.5</mn><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; /><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-45" style="width: 16.109em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 13.199em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1013.2em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-46"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-47" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">F<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-48" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-49" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.215em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1002.09em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.064em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-50"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-51" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-52" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-53" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-54" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">v</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.25em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.121em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-55" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.22em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.215em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-56" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-57" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-58" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">v</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-59" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-60" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.904em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.408em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-61"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-62" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">F<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-63" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.326em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-64" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.9em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.904em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-65" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-66" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">187.5</span><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-67" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.166em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-68" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-69"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-70" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-71"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-72"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-73" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-74" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>v</mi></mrow><mi>t</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>F</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><mi>m</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>187.5</mn><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-5">F = \frac{m \times \Delta v}{t} \Rightarrow \Delta v = \frac{Ft}{m} = 187.5 \, ms^{-1}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-26-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>N</mi><mi>t</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>500</mn><mn>60</mn></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>H</mi><mi>z</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8.33</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>H</mi><mi>z</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-275" style="width: 12.01em; </span>
                                    </div>

                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 10 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 160px; height: 105px;"></p>

<p>দুইটি নিরেট গোলক পরস্পরকে স্পর্শ করে আছে। স্পর্শ বিন্দুটিতে গোলকদ্বয়ের স্পর্শকের সাপেক্ষে পুরো সিস্টেমটির জড়তার ভ্রামক কত হবে, যখন গোলকদ্বয়ের ভর 1kg ও ব্যাসার্ধ&nbsp; 1m?</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>স্পর্শকের সাপেক্ষে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-31-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>I</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>G</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>7</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-330" style="width: 12.051em; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-336" style="font-size: 70.7%;                                         <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি বৃত্তাকার চাকতির ব্যাস&nbsp;4m। এটি 30&nbsp;সেকেন্ডে 45m&nbsp;পথ না পিছলিয়ে গড়িয়ে অতিক্রম করে। চাকতিটির কৌণিক গতিশক্তি কত? [ চাকতির ভর 1kg ]</p>

padding-left: 0.207em;">a</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-540" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-541" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-542" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">80</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-543" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-544" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">4.8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-545" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-546" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">384</span><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-547" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.166em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-548" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">N<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>W</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>80</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>4.8</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>384</mn><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>N</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-42">W = m(g-a) = 80 \times 4.8 = 384 \, N</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">

</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><strong><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-50-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>J</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>v</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>45</mn><mn>1000</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mn>45</mn><mn>1000</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0.225</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>k</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-628" style="width: 24.223em; </span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-51-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow><mfrac><mn>60</mn><mn>60</mn></mfrac></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>d</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-666" style="width: 9.1em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 7.461em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1007.22em, 2.994em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-667"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-668" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">ω</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-669" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-670" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-677" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-678" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; <p>Now,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-52-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>1.25</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>24.67</mn><mi>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-691" style="width: 18.158em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 14.879em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.945em, 1014.88em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-692"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-693" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">F<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-694" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-695" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-696"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.068em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-697" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">ω</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.617em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-698" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-699" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">r</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-700" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-701" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.5</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-702" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-703" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.297em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.158em, 1001.76em, 4.387em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-704"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-705" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-706"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-707" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-708" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-709" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.506em; left: 1.846em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-710" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-711" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-712" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">1.25</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-713" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-714" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">24.67</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-715" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">N<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.552em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>ω</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>1.25</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>24.67</mn><mi>N</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-52">F=m\omega^2r=0.5\times\left(2\pi\right)^2\times1.25=24.67N</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 18 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>15 kg&nbsp;ভরের একটি বস্তু মুক্তভাবে পড়ার সময় বাতাসের বাধা 8 N থাকলে লব্ধি ত্বরণ কত?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-62-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msup><mi>F</mi><mo>&amp;#x2032;</mo></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msup><mi>F</mi><mo>&amp;#x2032;</mo></msup></mrow><mi>m</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>15</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow><mn>15</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>9.267</mn><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1003.2em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 3.199em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-932" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-933" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">9.267</span><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-934" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.166em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-935" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-936"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-937" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-938"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-939"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-940" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-941" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>F</mi><mo>′</mo></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>F</mi><mo>′</mo></msup></mrow><mi>m</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>15</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow><mn>15</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>9.267</mn><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-62">ma = mg - F' \Rightarrow a = \frac{mg-F'}{m} = \frac{15 \times 9.8-8}{15} = 9.267 \, ms^{-2}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 19 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি রাস্তা 50m ব্যাসার্ধে বাঁক নিয়েছে। ঐ স্থানে রাস্তাটি 5m চওড়া এবং এর ভেতরের কিনারা হতে বাইরের কিনারা 0.5m উঁচু। সর্বোচ্চ কত বেগে ঐ স্থানে নিরাপদে বাঁক নেওয়া সম্ভব?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-67-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>0.5</mn><mi>m</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>5</mn><mi>m</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.1</mn><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; /></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-986" style="width: 13.814em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-993" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.641em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.52em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.777em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-994"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-995" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1000" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1001" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.1</span><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-1002" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.166em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1003" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 1.764em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1008"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1009"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1010" style="font-size: 70.7%; \,</script></span>&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-68-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1014" style="width: 0.453em; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-69-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>&amp;#x2245;</mo><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; /></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1017" style="width: 5.412em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.428em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1004.43em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1018"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1019" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1020" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1021" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1022" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1023" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;
