<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-70-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mi>r</mi><mi>g</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.1</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>50</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>49</mn><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1066" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">v</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1067" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1068" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">7</span><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-1069" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.166em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1070" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1071"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1072" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1073"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1074"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1075" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1076" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mi>r</mi><mi>g</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo>×</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>×</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.1</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>50</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>49</mn><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-70">tan\theta = \frac{v^2}{rg} \Rightarrow v^2 = tan\theta \times r \times g = 0.1 \times 50 \times 9.8 = 49 \, \therefore v =7 \, ms^{-1}</script></span></p>
</span>

                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-74-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi>m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>50</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>150</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>N</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>7500</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1110" style="width: 15.945em; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.41em, 4.305em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1175" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">μ</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1176" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.86em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.863em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1177" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1178" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">506.67</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1179" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1180" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">N<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.797em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.202em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>F</mi><mi>g</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>μ</mi><mi>g</mi></msub><mo>×</mo><mi>R</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>R</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>F</mi><mi>g</mi></msub><msub><mi>μ</mi><mi>g</mi></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>506.67</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>N</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-78">F_g=\mu_g\times R\Rightarrow R=\frac{F_g}{\mu_g}=506.67\ N</script></span></p>
</span>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 24 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি বৈদ্যুতিক পাখা স্থির অবস্থা থেকে 20 বার সম্পূর্ণ ঘূর্ণনের ফলে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-84-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>30</mn><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; /><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>d</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>/</mo></mrow><mi>s</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>c</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1242" style="width: 5.516em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.51em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1004.51em, 2.61em, -999.998em);                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.158em, 1000.29em, 4.387em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1333" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.371em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1334" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1335" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1336" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1338" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1339" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1340" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1341" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">α</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1342" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1343" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1344" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1345" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1346" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">20</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1347" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1348" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1349" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; margin-left: -0.531em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1352" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">900</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1356" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1357" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">20</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.13em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.133em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1358" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1359" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">3.58</span><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-1360" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.166em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1361" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">r</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1362" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1363" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">d<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-1364" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.166em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1365" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1366" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">e</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1367"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.395em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1368" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">c</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1369"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1370"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1371" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1372" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi>ω</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mi>ω</mi><mn>0</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>α</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>30</mn><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>0</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>α</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mo>×</mo><mn>20</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>α</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>900</mn><mrow><mn>4</mn><mi>π</mi><mo>×</mo><mn>20</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3.58</mn><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>d</mi><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>s</mi><mi>e</mi><msup><mi>c</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-89">\omega^2 = \omega^2_0 + 2\alpha\theta \Rightarrow (30)^2 = 0^2 + 2\alpha (2\pi \times 20) \Rightarrow \alpha = \frac{900}{4\pi \times 20} = 3.58 \, rad\,sec^{-2}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-91-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msub><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></mrow><mi>&amp;#x03B1;</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>188.49</mn></mrow><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1.047</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>180.03</mn><mi>s</mi><mo>&amp;#x2248;</mo><mn>3</mn><mspace width=&quot;thinmathspace&quot; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">ω</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1396" style="font-size: 50%; top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.064em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1404"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1405" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1406" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1.047</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.99em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.994em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1407" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1408" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">180.03</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1409" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1410" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">≈</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1411" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">3</span><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-1412" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.166em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1413" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1414" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">i</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1415" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.752em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>ω</mi><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>ω</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></mrow><mi>α</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>188.49</mn></mrow><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1.047</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>180.03</mn><mi>s</mi><mo>≈</mo><mn>3</mn><mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace><mi>m</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-91">t = \frac{\omega-\omega_0}{\alpha} = \frac{0-188.49}{-1.047} = 180.03s \approx 3 \, min</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

</span>

                                            <span>Question 21 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি নিরেট গোলকের ভর 3kg ও ব্যাসার্ধ 5m হলে, যেকোনো ব্যাসের সাপেক্ষে জড়তার ভ্রামক কত?</p>

                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-131-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mi>r</mi><mi>g</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>tan</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mi>r</mi><mi>g</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>tan</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mfrac><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>14</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>200</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>5.7</mn><mi>o</mi></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1791" style="width: 22.133em; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1848" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1849" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.682em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1001.27em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1850" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">5.7</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 1.273em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1851" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">o</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.789em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.847em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.402em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mi>r</mi><mi>g</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>∴</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>tan</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mi>r</mi><mi>g</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>tan</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mfrac><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>14</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>200</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>5.7</mn><mi>o</mi></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-131">tan\theta=\frac{v^2}{rg}\therefore\theta=\tan^{-1}{\left(\frac{v^2}{rg}\right)=\tan^{-1}{\frac{\left(14\right)^2}{200\times9.8}}}=5.7^o</script></span></p>
</span>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-137-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.25</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.75</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>66.62</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1878" style="width: 20.576em; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 24 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একই দিকে চলমান সমভরের দুটি বস্তু অস্থিতিস্থাপক সংঘর্ষে মিলিত হলে নিচের কোন লেখচিত্রটি সংঘর্ষে ক্ষয়প্রাপ্ত গতিশক্তি এবং বস্তুদ্বয়ের আপেক্ষিক বেগের সম্পর্ক নির্দেশ করে?</p>

                                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>গতিশক্তির ক্ষয় আপেক্ষিক বেগের বর্গের সমানুপাতিক।</p>

rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.342em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2060" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.727em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-2061"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2062"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2063" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">12</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 6.764em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -5.697em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 7.153em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>m</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msubsup><mi>v</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>+</mo><msubsup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mn>2</mn><mi>m</mi><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mi>m</mi><mrow><mo>{</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msubsup><mi>v</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>+</mo><msubsup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mo>}</mo></mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mi>m</mi><mrow><mo>{</mo><mrow><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mo>}</mo></mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mi>m</mi><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mi>m</mi><msubsup><mi>v</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>12</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></msubsup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-138">\frac{1}{2}m\left(v_1^2+v_2^2\right)-\frac{1}{2}2m\left(\frac{v_1+v_2}{2}\right)^2=\frac{1}{4}m\left\{2\left(v_1^2+v_2^2\right)-\left(v_1+v_2\right)^2\right\} \\
=\frac{1}{4}m\left\{\left(v_1+v_2\right)^2+\left(v_1-v_2\right)^2-\left(v_1+v_2\right)^2\right\} \\
=\frac{1}{4}m\left(v_1-v_2\right)^2=\frac{1}{4}mv_{12}^2 
</script></span></p>

<p>অর্থাৎ,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-139-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2206;</mo><msub><mi>E</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><msubsup><mi>v</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>12</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></msubsup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2064" style="width: 4.674em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.814em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1003.81em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2065"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2066" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">Δ</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2067"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2068" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">E<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2069" style="font-size: 70.7%; padding-left: 0.289em;">∝</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2071" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.273em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.342em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2073" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.727em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-2074"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2075"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2076" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">12</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 25 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>বোরের হাইড্রোজেন পরমাণু মডেলে একটি ইলেকট্রন একটি প্রোটনের চারদিকে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-140-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>5.2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2077" style="width: 7.602em; vertical-align: -0.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.402em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mi>r</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>9.1</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>31</mn></mrow></msup><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2.18</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>6</mn></msup></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>5.2</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>=</mo><mn>8.32</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>N</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-146">F=\frac{mv^2}{r}=\frac{9.1\times{10}^{-31}\times\left(2.18\times{10}^6\right)^2}{5.2\times{10}^{-11}}\ =8.32\times{10}^{-8}\ N </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-161-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi>v</mi></mrow><mi>t</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mfrac><mn>500</mn><mn>1000</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi>v</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>40</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2406" style="width: 19.018em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 15.576em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.494em, 1015.58em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2407"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2408" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">F<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2409" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-2410" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.682em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.56em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.777em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2411"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2412" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2413" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2414" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">v</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.68em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.682em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2416" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2417" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">10</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2418" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-2419" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.953em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1002.83em, 4.428em, -999.998em); top: -4.711em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.432em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2420"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-2421"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.109em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.74em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.342em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2422" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">500</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2425" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2426" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">v</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2428" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2429" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2430" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">v</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2431" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2432" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">40</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2433" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2434" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2435"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2436" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-2437"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2438"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2439" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2440" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.202em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>v</mi></mrow><mi>t</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mfrac><mn>500</mn><mn>1000</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>v</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>40</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-161">F=\frac{m\Delta v}{t}\Rightarrow10=\frac{\frac{500}{1000}\times\Delta v}{2}\Rightarrow\Delta v=40\ ms^{-1} </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 29 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>গাছ থেকে&nbsp;2kg&nbsp;ভরের একটি নারকেল সোজা নিচের দিকে পড়ছে। বাতাসের বাধা&nbsp;8.6N&nbsp;হলে নারকেলটির ত্বরণ কত?&nbsp;</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-166-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>=</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x2013;</mo><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#xD7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>8.6</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>a</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>=</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>5.5</mn><mi>m</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>/</mo></mrow><msup><mi>sec</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2486" style="width: 24.633em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 20.166em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1020.17em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2487"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2488" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2489" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">a</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2490" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2491" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2492" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2493" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2494" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2495" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2496" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">–</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2497" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.166em;">F<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2498" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2499" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2500" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">a</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2501" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2502" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2503" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2504" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">9.8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2505" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2506" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">8.6</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2507" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2508" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">a</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2509" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2510" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2511" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2512" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">5.5</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2513" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-2514"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2515"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2516" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">/</span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2517" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.723em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.27em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2518" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">sec</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 1.273em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2519" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.403em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>=</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>–</mo><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>8.6</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>a</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>=</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>5.5</mn><mi>m</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>/</mo></mrow><msup><mi>sec</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-166">ma\ =\ mg\ – F⇒ ma = 2× 9.8- 8.6   
\Rightarrow a\ =\ 5.5m/\sec^2 
</script></span></p>
</span>

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 30 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি গাড়ীর চাকা&nbsp;30 min&nbsp;এ&nbsp;2,000&nbsp;বার ঘুরে&nbsp;10km&nbsp;পথ অতিক্রম করে। চাকার পরিধি কত?</p>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি তলে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-172-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2586" style="width: 3.467em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.833em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.306em, 1002.83em, 2.349em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.357em; left: 0.486em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-2592"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2593"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2594" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2595" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>যেহেতু বস্তুটি সমবেগে চলমান তাই ত্বরণ/মোট বল শূন্য। গতিশীল অবস্থায় শুধু গতীয় র্ঘর্ষণ বল গতির বিপরীতে ক্রিয়া করে। তাই নীট বল শূন্য হতে হলে বস্তুর উপর প্রযুক্ত বল 5N হতে হবে।</p>
</span>

                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 32 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>অনুভূমিক দিকে গতিশীল&nbsp;2 kg&nbsp;ভরের একটি লৌহ গোলক&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-173-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>5</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2596" style="width: 3.802em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-178-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>f</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2206;</mo><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>16</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>k</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2658" style="width: 22.625em; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>τ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi>L</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo></mover></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>15</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>j</mi></mrow><mo>^</mo></mover></mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>6</mn><mi>t</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="false">^</mo></mover></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-191">\tau=\frac{d\ \vec{L}}{dt}=15\widehat{{j}}-6t\hat{k} </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-11-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-128" style="width: 10.781em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.814em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1008.57em, 2.666em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-129"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-130"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-132" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-137" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-138" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">M</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-139"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); font-family: MathJax_Main;">r</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.322em, 1000.95em, 4.264em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1000.37em, 1.232em, -999.998em); top: -1.678em; left: 0.576em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.07em, 1.191em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-150" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-283" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.198em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>22.5</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>45</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>°</mo></mrow></msqrt><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>15</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-20">\rm =\sqrt{22.5×10×tan\ 45°}ms^{-1}=15\ ms^{-1}</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-21-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mn>15</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>3.6</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>54</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-284" style="width: 13.158em;                                     </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.361em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.411em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-34">\rm [g=10\ ms^{-2}]</script></span></p>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-35-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>30</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>200</mn></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5000</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-495" style="width: 22.297em; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-499" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.904em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-525" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-526" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.752em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>30</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>200</mn></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5000</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-35">\rm a=\frac{V_r}{m}\frac{dm}{dt}-g\Rightarrow30=\frac{1000\times200}{m}-10\therefore m=5000\ kg</script></span></p>

<p>জ্বালানীসহ রকেটের ভর <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-36-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>5000</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-531" style="width: 3.322em; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-37-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mn>3000</mn><mn>200</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>15</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-537" style="width: 4.92em;                                                 <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-39-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>10</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-552" style="width: 4.237em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-43-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>60</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi></mrow><mn>60</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-596" style="width: 17.215em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 14.1em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1014.1em, 2.666em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-597"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-598" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">F</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-599" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-600" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-601" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">a</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-602" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-603" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-604" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-605" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">60</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-606" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-607" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.068em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.95em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.49em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-608"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-609" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-610" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">v</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-611" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">60</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.07em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.068em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-612" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-613" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-614" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">v</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-615" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-616" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-617" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-618" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-619"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-620" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-621"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-622"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-623" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-624" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>60</mn><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi></mrow><mn>60</mn></mfrac><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-43">\rm F=ma\Rightarrow2=60\times\frac{\Delta v}{60}\therefore\Delta v=2\ ms^{-1} </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 8 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-44-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-625" style="width: 2.2em; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-45-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-631" style="width: 5.963em; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-46-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-641" style="width: 3.132em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-47-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-647" style="width: 12.01em; top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-648"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-649" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">F</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-650" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-651" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-652"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.027em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.9em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.449em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-653"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-654" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">d</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-655" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.326em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-656"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-657" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">d</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-658" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.03em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.027em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-659" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-660" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-661" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-662" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-663"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-664" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-665" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-666" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-667" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-668" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">t</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-669" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-670" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">3</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-671" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span></span><span style="display: inline-block;
