display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-48-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>24</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-672" style="width: 10.002em; top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-673"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-674" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">F</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-675" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; </span>

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 10 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>2 kg ভর ও 30 cm&nbsp;দৈর্ঘ্যের একটি সুষম দন্ড এর প্রান্ত দিয়ে গমনকারী অক্ষের সাপেক্ষে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-57-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>4</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>/</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-778" style="width: 3.802em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.094em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1003.06em, 2.61em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">I</mi><mi>ω</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mo>×</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><mi>ω</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>0.3</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0.24</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-62">\rm L=I\omega=\frac{1}{3}\times m\times l^2\times\omega=\frac{1}{3}\times2\times{0.3}^2\times4=0.24\ kgm^2s^{-1} </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-49" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-50" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">c</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-51" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-52" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-53" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-54" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-55" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-56" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-57" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.747em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.202em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msqrt><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi></msub></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi><msqrt><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></msqrt></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msqrt><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi></msub></msqrt><mo>.</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></msqrt></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-2">\rm E_k=\frac{p^2}{2m}\Rightarrow\sqrt{E_k}=\frac{p}{\sqrt{2m}}\Rightarrow\sqrt{E_k}.\frac{1}{p}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2m}}= constant</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-14-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>0.9</mn><mrow><mn>20</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>45</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-224" style="width: 19.018em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 15.576em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1015.58em, 2.666em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-225"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-226" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">F</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-227" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-228" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-229" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">a</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-230" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-231" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">a</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-232" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-233" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.699em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.45em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.244em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-234" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">F</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.58em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.285em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-235" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.7em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-236" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-237" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">a</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-238" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-239" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.789em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.86em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.449em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-240" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.9</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.281em, 1002.67em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.523em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.309em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-241"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-242" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">20</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-243" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-244"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.395em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-245"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-246"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-247" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.301em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-248"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-249"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-250" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-251" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.79em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.789em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-252" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-253" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">45</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-254" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-255" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-256"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-257" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-258"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-259"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-260" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-261" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.802em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>0.9</mn><mrow><mn>20</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>45</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-14">\rm F=ma\Rightarrow a=\frac{F}{m}\Rightarrow a=\frac{0.9}{20\times{10}^{-3}}=45\ ms^{-2} </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 11 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>20kg ভর ও 0.20m ব্যাসার্ধের একটি বেলনাকার বস্তু <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-27-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>5</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-403" style="width: 3.653em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.982em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.306em, 1002.98em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-404"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-405" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-406" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-407" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-408"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.38em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.43em, 1000.37em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-409" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.357em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-410"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-411"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-412" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-413" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.089em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.139em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>5</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-27">\rm 5\ ms^{-1}</script></span> বেগে আনুভূমিক তলে গড়াতে থাকলে অক্ষের সাপেক্ষে জড়তার ভ্রামক–</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>

                                            <span>Question 12 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">6g ভরের একটি বস্তুকে 1.5m লম্বা সুতার প্রান্তে বেঁধে এ ঘুরালে সুতার টান কত?</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-33-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>17.42</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-479" style="width: 9.018em; top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-480"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-481" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-482" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>রাস্তার ব্যাংকিং নির্ভর করে–<br>
(i) গাড়ির দ্রুতির ওপর<br>
(ii) বাঁকের ব্যাসার্ধের ওপর<br>
(iii) গাড়ির ভরের ওপর&nbsp;<br>
<strong>নিচের কোনটি সঠিক?</strong></p>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-34-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-492" style="width: 5.248em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.305em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1004.3em, 2.83em, -999.998em); top: -2.211em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-493"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-494" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-495" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">t</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-496" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-497" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-498" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-499" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-500" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.781em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.322em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.326em;"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-501"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-502" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">v</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.26em; left: 0.371em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-503" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.78em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.781em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; </span>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 8 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">নিউটনের কোন গতিসূত্র বলের সাথে ভরবেগের পরিবর্তনের হারের সম্পর্ক স্থাপন করে?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">

                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">একটি গাড়ি স্থির অবস্থা হতে সমত্বরণে চলতে শুরু করলে সময়ের বিপরীতে ভরবেগের লেখচিত্র?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>সমত্বরণে v-t গ্রাফ এবং mv-t গ্রাফ একই রকম, শুধু ঢাল m গুণ হবে।</p>
